reviewText: I love the movies but the set did not contain the 4th movie, only 2 copies of the 3rd. I had to buy the fourth movie separately.
I loved the other Ringu movies, but i have to say i was disappointed with this one.
An incredibly good prequel to the Ringu series. It really adds a lot of depth the story.
I love the story behind the Ring.
Note: Audio is Japanese, not English as stated in the description. Subtitled in English, French, and Spanish.
